{"tid":790000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇人覺得走飲管呢樣野係弱智到一個極點","createTime":"2018-08-22T15:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T17:01:36.000Z","uid":136116,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95a45fdd1d18070ec869ea69c2d3bb41f9b1c9f7","tid":790000,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"好多人都覺得KFC走咗飲管對地球環境幫助好大乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bloomberg.com/amp/view/articles/2018-06-07/plastic-straws-aren-t-the-problem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Famp%2Fview%2Farticles%2F2018-06-07%2Fplastic-straws-aren-t-the-problem&d=EdlrfVf9YpEuVRMYBF2uLEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=744553c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bloomberg.com/amp/view/articles/2018-06-07/plastic-straws-aren-t-the-problem</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下上面篇文 但係我quote一個好重要嘅data出嚟<br />\n: 飲管佔海洋塑膠廢物嘅比例只有0.03%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/19/business/plastic-straws-ban-fact-check-nyt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2Fbusiness%2Fplastic-straws-ban-fact-check-nyt.html&d=EdlrfVf9YpEuVRMYBF2uLEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=77c7e820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/19/business/plastic-straws-ban-fact-check-nyt.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文章仲搞笑 有個研究話美國每年用500m枝飲管 但係原來個研究係一個9歲細佬做 而且個outcome係錯到離晒大譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有想講到嘅係<br />\n普通餐廳嚟講 首先我點知你個杯洗得乾唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 匙羹 筷子嗰啲你就話可以食之前拎杯水洗下 但係人地拎杯野飲過嚟你諗住點樣清潔個杯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔少飲品 例如珍珠奶茶 紅豆冰 檸檬茶 楊枝甘露等等 唔用飲管根本飲唔到 難道啲人要飲晒上面啲奶茶先飲到下面嘅珍珠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後就係想講 禁用飲管同杯蓋呢樣野其實係好反智嘅事<br />\n係人都知你kfc啲野飲係一早斟定先 杯野飲擺係度 唔用杯蓋蓋住 啲灰呀口水呀全部跌晒落去你再飲 爽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保撚係咁講話因為kfc走蓋走飲管所以會支持幫襯佢地 真係笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你個汽水杯內外嘅coating都係膠嘅 你食雞嘅手套都係膠嘅 食飯個兜? 餐具? 就連你拎嚟墊雞張紙都係膠嘅<br />\n<br />\n咁撚多可以replace到嘅野你唔去replace 你去禁用影響咁細嘅飲管杯蓋<br />\n一句講晒<br />\nKfc 同所有proclaim話要走飲管嘅機構都弱鳩智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6077beab0ab060e0f9d203e55f4773ac73d6c0ec","tid":790000,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"之前咪有人整左個意粉飲管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d495cc2c3baa129d3c7a0a58b6cba9cbc4c2dd","tid":790000,"uid":139873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b59cfa023ee9f7688cae77ec513c1509d668f2fe","tid":790000,"uid":136116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"同埋啱啱唔記得講<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1976695/邊飲邊食海藻飲管%20LOLISTRAW！救救地球零污染\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1976695%2F%E9%82%8A%E9%A3%B2%E9%82%8A%E9%A3%9F%E6%B5%B7%E8%97%BB%E9%A3%B2%E7%AE%A1%2520LOLISTRAW%EF%BC%81%E6%95%91%E6%95%91%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E9%9B%B6%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93&d=EdlrfVf9YpEuVRMYBF2uLEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a30f5dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1976695/邊飲邊食海藻飲管%20LOLISTRAW！救救地球零污染</a><br />\n<br />\n好似樓上巴打講意粉飲管咁<br />\n其實已經有人做埋海藻飲管出嚟 而且因為海藻生長週期好快 同埋可以吸收好多CO2 所以理論上你用得越多種得越多海藻 對環境其實係更加好<br />\n<br />\n但係問題係好多環保撚覺得 如果呢樣野未普及嘅話 最好就完全唔用飲管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死人"},{"pid":"bca87015e97a402c173f7ac3e371586e4bdec3c1","tid":790000,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"佢地完全無視飲管嘅作用<br />\n淨係識問點解要用 <br />\n俾冰掂到牙 就叫你走冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食炸雞手污糟 就叫你整污糟隻杯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔諗下實際用kfc個軟林林杯飲 開口大又軟 啲可樂好易漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ded0b612a5f045c46abb12695180dc9bc9c4eba","tid":790000,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"搬咗去隔離時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家可以入嚟玩下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/790015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/790015</a>"},{"pid":"5f1be63ca9c2c1cd0d6c987e1d4b1f36ed5152fb","tid":790000,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bca87015e97a402c173f7ac3e371586e4bdec3c1","tid":790000,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"佢地完全無視飲管嘅作用<br />\n淨係識問點解要用 <br />\n俾冰掂到牙 就叫你走冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食炸雞手污糟 就叫你整污糟隻杯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔諗下實際用kfc個軟林林杯飲 開口大又軟 啲可樂好易漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"的確 其實諗下其他辦法仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你肯換晒啲餐具我相信更加有效同埋唔會太多人反對"},{"pid":"60f38524b1a299efddc2d356fc24db2a19a1db27","tid":790000,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"其實d飲管整短d得唔得？"},{"pid":"fa67b9cb8a5271fa073705e2f46b0d35ff8fb5ef","tid":790000,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f38524b1a299efddc2d356fc24db2a19a1