9c1bd7f96376","tid":790000,"uid":101917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啲環保撚真係冇乜腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫人走乜走物 又唔提供啲可行嘅解決方法 淨係識用啲弱撚智方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食屎啦！最環保就係食屎啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}